metadata.name: Trip to Nara
metadata.description:
During my trip to Japan, I visited Nara. At the train station, you stand in front of these amusingly painted stairs advertising the city as a tourist destination. 

This background is the setting for the "Journey to Nara" of our two protagonists: a late girl and a coffee-loving boy. Will this journey lead to romance?
